🔗 HOW POLYGON IS USED (CLEAR & SIMPLE)

Polygon is the access controller + payment settlement layer.

Smart Contract Stores:

File ID (CID hash)

Owner (creator)

Price (USDC)

Expiry timestamp

Download limit

Paid status

Smart Contract Handles:

Receiving USDC from SideShift

Splitting payment:

Creator

Platform fee

Enforcing rules:

if (paid && notExpired && downloadsLeft)
   grantAccess();

🔁 HOW SIDESHIFT IS USED (VERY IMPORTANT)

SideShift is your cross-chain payment engine.

You use SideShift to:

Accept BTC / ETH / SOL / BNB / LTC / etc.

Convert everything into Polygon USDC

Avoid bridges & liquidity issues

Give users frictionless checkout

Technical Flow:

Frontend → SideShift API (create shift)

SideShift → returns deposit address

User sends crypto

SideShift → sends USDC to Polygon contract

Contract emits event → unlock file

👉 You never custody funds
👉 No bridge risks
👉 Very hackathon-friendly

